### Authentication Tests

### Register User
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_data": {
    "username": "testuser",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "SecurePass123!",
    "full_name": "Test User",
    "bio": "A test user for development"
  }
}

### Login User (capture token)
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

> {%
client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.token.accessToken);
%}

### Login with Email
POST http://user-management.local/api/v1/user-management/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

